                <h1>Peel and Stick Wallpaper vs. Prepasted: Which One to Choose?</h1>
                <p>Peel and stick wallpaper offers a convenient way to update your space without glue or water. Simply peel off the backing and stick it to your wall, making it perfect for renters. In contrast, prepasted wallpaper requires water for application and is often more traditional. Consider your project needs when choosing between them.</p>
